    "However, for applications such as freedom-to-operate and prior-art search, recall is arguably the most critical metric 1.",
    "This is where PatCID has an advantage.",
    "Automatically-generated databases are also claimed to be facing the limitation that key compounds may be hard to find among all annotated compounds, which include solvents, radicals, or fragments 11.",
